cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with video analysis and skill determination, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of attention modules and ranking loss function suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The evaluation of the proposed method on two datasets, including one from YouTube, suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
